<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Class Payment Reminder</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .logo img {
      max-width: 200px;
    }

    .content {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .button {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .button a {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="https://escraowme.cyclic.app/rahmoun-logo1.png" alt="Your Group Logo">
      <h2>Class Payment Reminder</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
      <p>This is a reminder that you need to repay the class fees before the next lesson in {{className}}. Failure to do so will result in restricted access to the class.</p>
      <p>Please ensure that you complete the payment as soon as possible to avoid any inconvenience.</p>
      <p>If you have already made the payment, please disregard this message.</p>
      <p>Thank you for your cooperation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="button">
      <a href="{{url}}">Repay Now</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Username: {{name}}</p>
      <p>Group Name: {{className}}</p>
      <p>&copy; 2023 Your Group. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
